<br>
The Book of Charm and Sacrifice<br>
Plane of Sky - Found on the right table near an Efreeti spawn. (1295, 558, -762) - (Spawn time: 24 hours)<br>
<br>
As I've never been to PoS, I'm wondering if someone can point me to a map of the plane, or any info at all.<br>
<br>
1) Do I need to fight to this spot or is it a benign quest plane?<br>
2) If fighting, is it in some obscure place that I'll prolly never see?<br>
3) To those that have looted the book, or have seen it, was it there most of the times you've been to PoS?<br>
<br>
I'm hoping that you plucky rogues can offer some insight. They say druids are the masters of travel, but in my book Rogues make the best explorers of dungeons. Rogues have seen nooks and crannies that a butt-sitting druid would never dream of seeing. Cheers and thanks for any help.<br>
<br>
Lantris<br>
Karana <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucedea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cedea</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home1.gte.net/res02go8/cillatiny.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/22/01 11:59:49 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter Epic - PoS Drop</span><hr size=1> The book is located in the quest hall.  You zone up, buy the 1cp key, and go to the northernmost <?can't remember for sure> portal, and click.<br>
<br>
Once you're in the quest hall, it's on the table in the rear left corner. It just looks like a book. It has a 24 hour spawn time, so just depends whether somone has been to get it or not.<br>
<br>
The quest hall is all non-aggro, as is the first island, so no fighting necessary.  Good luck.<br>
<br>
Cedea<br>
35th rogue<br>
