<br>
With the book being in a non-Kos place you can always just camp at table <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
This way it will be a one time trip but of course you will be out of the expgrind untill you get the book.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uayashii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ayashii</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/23/01 4:13:21 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter Epic - PoS Drop</span><hr size=1> 250pp is the cost of the sky gem that's required as reagent, your guild wiz has nothing to gain from that 250pp. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umomus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Momus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/23/01 2:32:00 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter Epic - PoS Drop</span><hr size=1> duh  camping! Geesh I think I left my brain at the shop for repairs.<br>
